The Student Management System is a beginner-to-intermediate level Python project designed to manage student records efficiently using file handling and object-oriented programming (OOP) concepts.
This project allows users to add, view, search, and delete student records through a simple menu-driven interface.
It demonstrates fundamental Python programming concepts widely used in real-world applications such as data storage, record management, and basic automation systems.
Responsiblites:
Add new student record
View all student records
Search student by roll number
Delete student record
Data stored permanently in file
Simple and user-friendly menu system
